These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, train, scooter, bike
1. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
2. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
3. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the bike and the person driving the train##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |     3      |  4   |
| Transport   | bike | bus | train | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, photography, skydiving, chess
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
2. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |       4       |
| Hobby   | board-games | chess | photography | skydiving |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, bartender, firefighter, mechanic
1. the bartender is on the right of the firefighter##1
2. the bartender is on the far left or far right##3
3. the dancer is the dancer##1
4. the dancer is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job   | mechanic | dancer | firefighter | bartender |

 #################################

 
