3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | singing | video-games | skydiving | puzzles |

